dcterms:description: CSI measurements collected in a residential area using a channel sounder, providing channel frequency responses between a moving single-antenna transmitter and a fixed receiver with an 8x8 patch antenna array.
dcterms:title: CSI measurements from a channel sounder

dcterms:description: A real-world dataset used for evaluating fingerprint-based positioning methods in massive MIMO systems, showing improved positioning accuracy with learned similarity metrics.
dcterms:title: Real-world CSI dataset
